| Feature             | OSI Model                     | TCP/IP Model                      |
| ------------------- | ----------------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| Layers              | 7                             | 4                                 |
| Use                 | Conceptual, teaching & design | Practical, real-world Internet    |
| Development         | ISO standard                  | Department of Defense (DoD)       |
| Layer Functions     | Separate layers for all tasks | Some layers combined              |
| Application Layer   | Only interacts with software  | Includes Presentation & Session   |
| Transport Protocols | TCP & UDP                     | TCP & UDP                         |
| Real-world Usage    | Rarely implemented fully      | Fully implemented on the Internet |
| Approach            | Vertical, theoretical         | Practical, functional             |
